## Phase 5: Baselines

### Baseline 1: TF-IDF + Edit Distance
- Represent equations as LaTeX strings
- TF-IDF for text
- Cosine similarity

### Baseline 2: TangentCFT
- State-of-the-art math retrieval system
- Tree-based representation + fastText embeddings

### Baseline 3: SciBERT (text-only)
- Ignore equation structure
- Treat LaTeX as text tokens
- Standard BERT embedding

### Baseline 4: Equation Embeddings (Krstovski & Blei, 2018)
- Reproduce their unsupervised method
- Compare with our contrastive approach

### Baseline 5: Random Embeddings
- Sanity check: Random projections should fail

